message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CC. The paper discusses a new dataset for machine comprehension that requires reasoning using commonsense knowledge, specifically script knowledge. This falls under the sub-category of natural language processing and understanding, which is covered by cs.CL. The paper also discusses the use of crowdsourcing for data collection, which could fall under cs.AI or cs.LG. The dataset could also be relevant for information retrieval (cs.IR) and computational cognition (cs.CC) research.
